name: laborer
description: He's a sweaty looking laborer.
talk: I'm busy, so stay outta my way.

name: vagrant
description: He ain't got nothing but himself.
talk: <Hic!> Ya gott summ beer? <Hic!>

name: scribe
description: He carries in his hand a bunch of small books and scrolls.
talk: <Yawn> You bore me

name: nobleman
description: This guy's probably never worked a day in his life.
talk: I spit on thee, you working-class knave.

name: bowyer
description: He's made so many bows in his day that he practically looks like one.

name: merchant
description: She's a typical seedy-looking street-merchant.
talk: Care to buy an apple?

name: sailor
description: He must be on leave from his ship in the Boraspian Sea.
talk: Aye, where's the bordello?

name: peasant
description: The poor old sap probably learned to tie his shoes at age 18.

name: monk
description: This monk has obviously been cooped up in a monastery too long. Pale as a sheet

name: criminal
description: This hardened criminal has a small knife, and looks desperate.
talk: hey asshole, give me all your money.  *spit*

name: warrior
description: This warrior would make a most potent adversary.
talk: You'll regret fighting me!

name: paladin
description: This righteous warrior stares down at you condescendingly.
talk: It is my sincere hope that you have made your peace with God.

name: ranger
description: This solitary ranger blends in so well with his surroundings you hardly see him
talk: <hmph>

name: knight
description: The regal knight stands before you, suited completely in glimmering armor.
talk: Greetings! Hail and well met, young one!

name: mercenary
description: She is a battle-worn mercenary, looking for her next easy kill.

name: giant rat
description: The rat's looking for food, and he thinks you're it!
talk: <squeak>

name: ghost
description: The ghost is nearly shapeless, so you cannot make out who it might be.
talk: Boo!

name: apparition
description: It's an apparition of a wrinkled old woman.
talk: WooooooOOOooooooooooo

name: evil wraith
description: The wraith stands before you with globs of flesh dripping from its bones
talk: Beware. I come to kill.

name: little mouse
description: He's hoping he doesn't get his tail cut off by the farmer's wife.
talk: <squeak>!

name: old gardener
description: The extremely old man is busy raking the lawn of the ominous house.
talk: I rake, I hoe, I walk, I mow.  It's my job, you know?

name: ghoul
description: He has blood dripping from his mouth - probably that of his last victim.
talk: Ha Ha Ha! I can smell your blood.  You're next

name: ghast
description: The ghast appears as a horrifying apparition of a dead man.
talk: Boo!

name: madman
description: This wild madman looks like he was someone's failed experiment.
talk: You die sucker!

name: dwarf
description: Although quite small, this dwarf can be a tough adversary
talk: Are you making fun of me?

name: minotaur
description: This wild creature has a horn on its forehead.
talk: <growl>

name: swordmaster
description: The swordsman guild has certified him a master craftsman.
talk: I'll cut you up fast.

name: centaur
description: You see a man, a horse, or both?
talk: get your hands off my ass!

name: guard
description: This guard looks like he's made out of rock.  You better do what he says.
talk: hey you, get the hell outta here!

name: headless horseman
description: You know... like the one who haunted Ichabod Crane.
talk: Ha!  And you thought I wouldn't be able to talk!

name: spectre
description: The spectre is a demonic-looking creature, dark as a shadow.
talk: Your soul is mine.

name: skeleton
description: The skeleton is an animated pile of bones.
talk: Die, fool

name: vampire
description: You know it's a vampire simply by seeing its protruding incisors.
talk: I vant to suck your blood!

name: warg
description: The warg stares at you from vacant eyes.
talk: WooooOOOooo

name: the ghost of Evan Nildredge
description: He was once the owner of this mansion, but now is merely a ghost.
talk: Oh how I long to live in this abode as a living being once again.

name: zombie
description: Flesh hangs loosely from his bones as he wanders aimlessly toward you.
talk: MmmmmmmmMMMmm

name: looter
description: He's got a sack draped over his shoulder, ready to loot anything in sight.
talk: Get out of my way, you amateur.

name: ghostly fencer
description: This ghost appears as a fencer, fully decked out in fencer's garb.
talk: En Guarde!

name: sewer rat
description: It's covered in sewer-goop.
talk: <growl>

name: lillianril
description: The tall plant-like creature stares at you through 18 eye-stalks.
talk: <pht>

name: dervish
description: The dervish is a small, swarthy-looking thief.
talk: Hand it over, fool

name: orc
description: The orc is a perversion of the elven race.
talk: you're not an elf, are you?  I hate elves!

name: worker
description: She's just a typical sewer worker doing typical sewer work.
talk: Don't worry, you get used to the smell.

name: thief
description: You almost didn't see him.  He blends in with his surroundings quite well.
talk: Cross me, and die

name: kobold
description: The kobold appears as a sort of upright-walking dog creature.
talk: Bark!

name: carrion crawler
description: The carrion crawler is a large multiped with a large mouth for eating flesh.
talk: <phhht>

name: pugilist
description: The pugilist fights only with his hands, but he does quite well with them.
talk: Put yer dukes up!

name: deadly kraken
description: The kraken is like an octopus, only 20 times larger.
talk: HOW DARE YOU DISTURB MY HUMBLE ABODE!

name: grinning demon
description: The demon has an evil grin etched in its blackened face.
talk: You have certainly come to grant me your soul.

name: gray elf
description: The most noble and intelligent of the elven-kind
talk: Greetings great warriors.  May luck be with you on your quest

name: drow elf
description: Deadly black elf.  You can hardly see him in the shaddows.
talk: How dare you invade my lair.  Leave now or be destroyed.

name: lich
description: A powerful lich stares at you with a hypnotic eye.
talk: Come with me to the underworld.  I will take you there.

name: hydra
description: A seven headed hydra looks at you.  You hope she has already eaten.
talk: Won't you be my guest for dinner.  I haven't had humans in a long time.

name: efreeti
description: An evil efreeti stares down at you in disgust.
talk: You dare to challenge the elemental plane of fire?!?

name: black dragon
description: A rather large black lizard stares at you.
talk: Hmmm...should I eat you now or save you for dinner.

name: brass dragon
description: You see a small glimmering dragon.  Doesn't look like it could hurt a fly.
talk: What is your purpose?

name: blue dragon
description: You see a large and angry looking blue dragon.
talk: I'm in a pissed off mood....prepare to die.

name: green dragon
description: You see a hideous looking green dragon as it swoops down upon you.
talk: It is a good day to die.

name: half-elf
description: This elf is larger than you're used to.  He must be half-human.
talk: All I do is clean up after you humans.  Can't you be more courteous?

name: waitress
description: You see a cute waitress holding a tray of drinks.
talk: Can I get you something to drink?

name: aristocrat
description: You see an aristocrat, one of the mayor's personal friends.
talk: I fart in your general direction.

name: dikumud ripoff
description: You see the stupid dikumud ripoff.
talk: Don't tell me you want money too.

name: bartender
description: You see a master bartender mixing and serving up drinks.
talk: What'll yew have, m'friend?

name: drunk
description: He smells and looks quite disgusting.
talk: <Hick!>

name: rabbit
description: You see a cute little bunny rabbit, with long ears.

name: troll
description: You see a very ugly troll, with a wide mouth full of sharp teeth.
talk: you look good enough to eat, except you stink so bad you turn my stomach!

name: hermit
description: You see a reclusive hermit.  He probably hasn't had a shower for 10 years.
talk: Go away!  I don't want any of your girl scout cookies!

name: mountain hiker
description: You see a mountain hiker enjoying a brisk walk in the mountains.
talk: Don't go across the bridge...the troll's pretty mean.

name: street-hiker
description: You see a city person hiking in the mountains.  He looks lost.
talk: How do I get back to the city?

name: air giant
description: You see the great air giant of the mountains.
talk: What are you foolish humans doing so far away from home?

name: soothsayer
description: You see an old man telling fortunes.
talk: Beware the ides of march

name: scorpion
description: You see a large scropion whose stinging tail will poison you.

name: wombat
description: A giant furry bat swoops down upon you.
talk: < what are you trying to talk to a wombat for? >

name: vampire bat
description: You see a rather large black vampire bat coming at you very fast.

name: abominable snowman
description: You see a very large monster.  He looks like a giant snowman.
talk: Grrrrrrrr!!!

name: strumpet
description: You see a sleezy looking woman displaying herself proudly.
talk: Looking for a good time?

name: gambler
description: You see a rather large gambling man playing poker.
talk: Wanna lose some money to me buddy?  Let's play poker.

name: bouncer
description: You see a VERY large, gorilla-like person who doesn't like you being here.
talk: Get out and don't come back.

name: angry drunk
description: This guy smells like he just drank the entire keg of ale behind the bar.
talk: Get out of my way...I need a drink.

name: innkeeper
description: You see the innkeeper.  He runs this tavern.
talk: Sorry, no more rooms available.

name: caretaker
description: You see an old caretaker taking care of the graves.
talk: Beware of the Mausoleum...once you go in, you can never get out.

name: mummy of dabin
description: You see the mummified remains of Dabin, founder of the city of Caledonia.
talk: I cannot rest until Caledonia is returned to the elves.

name: loch ness monster
description: You see a rather LARGE sea serpent heading your way.
talk: Ha...you thought I was a myth, didn't you.

name: barracuda
description: You see a large, shark-like fish approaching you.
talk: blurp

name: large crayfish
description: This crayfish is so big, it looks like a lobster.

name: cave explorer
description: You see a person exploring the caves with you.
talk: Keep away from the lake.  You can't possibly survive in there.

name: evil high priestess
description: You see a rather tall, very evil looking priestess looking at you evily.
talk: Come sacrifice yourself to the gods.

name: grizzly bear
description: You see a rather large, black, grizzly bear who probably hasn't eaten in days.
talk: Grrrrrr.

name: mountain lion
description: You see a deadly mountain lion about to pounce on you.
talk: Growlll...

name: otyugh
description: You see a hideous creature with two tentacle arms protruding from his body.
talk: Mmmmmm.....fresh meat!

name: white dragon
description: You see a glimmering white dragon, as white as the snow on the mountains.
talk: I've come to heat things up in here.

name: red dragon
description: You see a dragon as red as the fires of hell.
talk: Don't mess with me, buddy, or you'll be toast.

name: bronze dragon
description: You see a dragon of glimmering bronze.
talk: Peace to those who battle against evil.

name: silver dragon
description: You see a very large, glimmering, silver dragon.
talk: Don't mess with me...I'm in a bad mood.

name: gold dragon
description: You see a very large, chinese, golden dragon...the most powerful good dragon.
talk: I will help you in your quest to purge evil.

name: Tiamat's body
description: You see Tiamat, the greatest of all evil dragons.

name: the white head of Tiamat
description: You see the white head of Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.
talk: If you can't take the heat, stay out of the kitchen.

name: the black head of Tiamat
description: You see the black head of Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.
talk: This is what you get for fooling around with me.

name: the green head of Tiamat
description: You see the green head of Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.
talk: Hahaha...You will never descend into the second level of Hell.

name: the blue head of Tiamat
description: You see the blue head of Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.
talk: I'll put a shock into your system.

name: the red head of Tiamat
description: You see the red head of Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.
talk: Go directly to hell...do not pass go...do not collect 200 gold pieces.

name: elven guard
description: For an elf, this guard is rather tall and strong.  Almost looks human.
talk: peace on your journey, my friend

name: mountain climber
description: You see a rugged mountain climber preparing to climb one of these mountains.
talk: I'm going up!  Care to join me?

name: the Fenris Wolf
description: You see a deadly, large, wolf-like creature lunging at you.

name: the Platinum Dragon
description: You see Bahamut, the Platinum Dragon.
talk: Only with this key can you defeat Tiamat, the Chromatic Dragon.

name: vorpal bunny
description: You see a small white rabbit.  This is the guardian to the caves of Aaaaahhhh?
talk: You must prove your worth to enter the caves of Aaaaahhhh.

name: french taunter
description: You see an obnoxious frenchman taunting you.
talk: I fart in your general direction.

name: harpy
description: You see an eagle-like creature with a human face.

name: griffon
description: You see a flying lion-like creature.

name: mountain raider
description: You see a large, ugly looking person running towards you rapidly.
talk: Give me all your money now!

name: wizard's apprentice
description: You see a young wizard's apprentice who is practicing his master's magic.
talk: Go away unless you want to get hurt.  Magic is a very powerful weapon.

name: lamia
description: You see a creature with an upper body of a human female.
talk: You shall be destroyed.

name: spirit naga
description: You see a snake-like creature with a humanoid female's head.
talk: I'll thrive on your blood...give it to me.

name: doppleganger
description: The doppleganger is a shift-shaper that has mutated to look like you.
talk: I've come to take your place in this world.

name: dryad
description: You see a beautiful and alluring tree sprite.
talk: beware of the circle of trees.  It is the source of great evil.

name: crow
description: The crow is large due to its feasting on giant rats.
talk: Caw!

name: bear
description: The brown bear is large and hungry.  He eyes you as perhaps his next meal.
talk: Grrrrrowl

name: field laborer
description: The laborer is plowing his fields, hoping for a large harvest.
talk: Smells like rain!

name: farmer's wife
description: This woman is sure homely!
talk: That's right... the one who cut off the mouse tails with a carving knife.

name: pixie
description: The small spritely pixie flutters about in the air around your ear.
talk: Your zipper is undone! hee hee

name: farmer
description: He's decked out in overalls and a hoe, sorta like that famous painting.
talk: Ya know anything about growing those things they call pee nuts?

name: raccoon
description: This masked bandit is probably trying to steal some of the farmer's crops.

name: bandit
description: You see a dusty, dirty bandit that's trying to take all your money.
talk: Give my your money NOW!

name: Countess Brianna
description: You see a tall, young woman dressed in a black, collared robe.
talk: I haven't had visitors in ages...why don't you come a little closer.

name: guard captain
description: You see commanding guard staring down at you.
talk: Don't bother me, I'm busy.

name: butcher
description: You see a butcher slicing meat for the dinner reception tonight.
talk: Watch it or you'll lose your fingers.

name: master chef
description: You see a chef preparing dinner.
talk: Get out of my kitchen you peasant pig-dog!

name: guard commander
description: You see the commander of the guards on patrol.
talk: Do not fear if you have official business here, but I do not believe you do.

name: palace guard
description: You see a palace guard standing at attention.
talk: What can I do for you?

name: monster
description: You see some labratory experiment that has gone wrong.
talk: Help me...

name: giant octopus
description: A giant octopus is attacking your boat.

name: sea dragon
description: You see a giant sea dragon with its head reared high out of the water.

name: rakshasa
description: You see a lion-like creature devouring his victim's flesh.
talk: Care to join me for dinner?

name: guardian ghost
description: You see a transparent ghost looking down at you.
talk: Away!  Leave me in peace!

name: black cave worm
description: You see a disgustingly smily yet huge worm burrowing its way towards you.

name: red cave worm
description: You see a giant red earthworm burrowing towards you.

name: grave digger
description: You see a dirty grave digger digging a grave in the cemetary.
talk: Can't you let the dead rot in peace?!?

name: gardener
description: You see an old gardener taking care of the grounds.
talk: Don't walk on the grass!

name: fire demon
description: You see a demon whose bright flames blind you.
talk: Hehehehehe...more victims.

name: gargoyle
description: You see a ferocious mystical-looking beast.

name: kopoacinth
description: You see an aquatic gargoyle-like creature swimming towards you.

name: wight
description: You see a disgusting humanoid form attacking you.
talk: Prepare to die mortal scum!

name: white unicorn
description: You see a magestic, powerful white unicorn with a great horn on its head.
talk: Leave in peace and all will be forgiven.

name: black unicorn
description: You see a majestic black unicorn with a great horn on its head.
talk: Leave in peace and no harm will come to you.

name: mounted knight
description: You see a royal knight mounted on his horse.
talk: Peace and success on your mission.

name: dragon guardian
description: You see a ferocious dragon guard who doesn't like you being here.
talk: Prepare for battle, human.

name: phantom dragon
description: You see a transparent dragon-like creature coming in your direction
talk: Be gone intruders of the sacred burial grounds of the dragons!

name: dragon's ghost
description: You see the tortured image of a deceased dragon.
talk: Go!  Leave me in peace!

name: phantom ghoul
description: You see a transparent ghoul screaming at you.

name: hunchback servant
description: You see an ugly looking creature with rounded shoulders creeping towards you.
talk: What are you doing in here?  The professor won't like that.

name: dungeon guard
description: You see a large guard running towards you.
talk: You are in an unauthorized zone...prepare to die!

name: inquisitioner
description: You see an inquisitioner trying to get information out of a prisoner.
talk: No one expects the Spanish Inquisition!

name: the crypt keeper
description: You see a devilish looking creature guarding the crypts of the mausoleum.
talk: Come here...let me tell you a story.

name: mad scientist
description: You see an evil mad scientist working on his experiments.
talk: Come join us...I could use a spare brain.

name: dungeon cook
description: The dungeon cook is throwing together some dinner for the prisoners.
talk: Wait in line for yer grub!

name: prisoner
description: You see a helpless prisoner of the palace dungeon.
talk: Help me...

name: prison guard
description: You see a large prison guard taunting you.
talk: A couple years in here will teach you some respect.

name: carp dragon
description: You see a mystical creature with the body of a carp and head of a dragon.

name: the ghost of Deneb
description: You see the ghost of Deneb, the first prominate mage of the Keslar family.
talk: Go mighty warriors and rid the house of Keslar from the evil possessing it.

name: cyclops
description: You see a giant humanoid with only one eye.
talk: Those who wish to steal my treasure will surely perish

name: the ghost of Rowland
description: You see the ghost of Rowland, the last great mage of Keslar.
talk: Destroy the evil which lurks in the palace.

name: restless mage ghost
description: You see a troubled ghost who cannot rest.
talk: I shall not rest until Keslar is freed from the evil which holds it.

name: crypt rat
description: You see a medium sized crypt rat eating at some old bones.
talk: Sqeeeeek.

name: librarian
description: You see an old librarian dusting off some of the books.
talk: Shhhh....this is a library.

name: visiting dignitary
description: You see a wise and powerful dignitary conversing with the mages.
talk: Go away you petty excuse for a warrior.

name: prestidigitator
description: You see a powerful prestidigitator showing off his magical talents.
talk: Come here, my friend, and I'll make you disappear.

name: necromancer
description: You see a powerful wizard testing out his powerful new spells.
talk: Come to the Arena.  We're testing some new spells on the prisoners.

name: sorceress
description: You see a beautiful mage with more powers than you can even dream of.
talk: Go away...I'm busy.

name: occultate
description: You see a master of the divine and unknown.
talk: Death to those who oppose the ways of Keslar.

name: giant venus fly-trap
description: You see a huge venus fly-trap that looks VERY hungry.

name: dining hall maid
description: You see a maid serving dinner to the people in the dining hall.
talk: I need to get this food to the mages or they'll be very angry.

name: butler
description: You see a tall butler cleaning up the mess you've made.
talk: I'm quite busy...why don't you go talk to the maids.

name: maid
description: You see a maid who looks like her feet hurt.
talk: all I do is scrub and fetch.  Someday I may kill someone.

name: wheat harvester
description: You see a dirty man hauling wheat back and forth through the fields.
talk: Can't you people do more than just sit there and stare?

name: master assassin
description: He's dressed completely in black from head to toe.
talk: Don't even think about it.

name: druid initiate
description: You see a druid initiate of the third circle meditating under a tree.
talk: How may I help you?

name: druid initiate
description: You see a druid initiate of the fifth circle meditating near a brook.
talk: Wisdom, my friend, is earned, not obtained.

name: master druid initiate
description: You see a druid initiate of the tenth circle.
talk: Class begins promptly at dawn.  Please be on time.

name: druid
description: You see a powerful druid of full rank studying some scrolls.
talk: The mythical philosopher's stone will bring life to the dead.

name: archdruid
description: You see a powerful archdruid who teaches all who will listen.
talk: You can learn much from the great druids of Etolos.

name: the Great Druid
description: You see the master of all druids of Etolos.
talk: If it is wisdom that you seek, perhaps I may be of assistance.

name: druidian guard
description: You see an angry druid running towards you.
talk: How dare you invade the inner circle of Etolos!

name: lumberjack
description: You see a lumberjack holding an axe and wearing women's clothing.
talk: I'm a lumberjack, and I'm OK.  I sleep all night and I work all day.

name: forest sprite
description: You see a beautiful forest sprite running through the forest.
talk: Hahaha...can't catch me!

name: farm helper
description: You see a young farmhand wearing jeans and carrying a shovel.
talk: did you come to help us with the harvest?

name: the Great Wizard
description: You see an old man who is probably more powerful than your entire party.
talk: Who dares to interrupt me in my own chambers?!?

name: tree sprite
description: You see a beautiful tree sprite jumping through the trees of the forest.
talk: The Enchanted Forest holds many wonders, but none you can see.

name: treant
description: You see a large tree in front of you that appears to be moving and talking!
talk: Wonders never cease in the Enchanted Forest!

name: nymph
description: You see a beautiful nymph teasing you.
talk: You wouldn't hit a defenseless woman, would you?

name: ogre
description: You see a giant ogre peering down at your puny body.
talk: So mister girly-man, you want to fight me?  Take your best shot!

name: leprechaun
description: You see a little green man carrying around a pot of gold.
talk: Just like a human to pick on us little people.

name: ravenous beast of Traal
description: You see a hideous creature of an origin you don't care to find out.
talk: You shouldn't be talking to me, you should be running away.

name: lycanthrope
description: You see a large, beautiful fox-like creature that is about to rip your head offHmmm...Haven't had Humans for dinner for a long time.
talk: Hmmm...Haven't had Humans for dinner for a long time.

name: vulture
description: You see a large scavenger bird swooping down at you.
talk: I prefer my food well-done, but you'll have to do.

name: sand worm
description: You see one of the deadliest creatures of the desert.

name: ermordenung
description: You see a tall female of surpassing beauty eying you curiously.
talk: Come taste the Kiss of Death!

name: traveling minstrel
description: You see a young bard with a mandolin singing a song.
talk: Would you like to hear a story about Lord Itinar?

name: cold drake
description: It's a small dragon-like creature, frosted and white.
talk: Chirp!

name: sewer orc
description: You see an ugly orc running towards you with a dagger.
talk: Grunt!

name: gypsy-bard
description: You see an attractive woman playing a musical instrument and dancing around.
talk: Come dance with me

name: herald
description: You see one of Lord Mandrake's heralds, probably delivering news.
talk: Please do not delay me, m'lord.  I am in haste to get to the castle.

name: blade
description: You see an experienced bard trained in the field of killing.
talk: Give me your gold and I might spare your life, if I'm in a good mood.

name: skald
description: You see a large Viking-type warrior just off from a recent raid.
talk: You dare to insult me by talking to me?

name: jongleur
description: You see a rogue juggling swords and dagger, trying to impress people.
talk: I can juggle anything you give me.

name: meistersinger
description: You see a singer of tales and mighty epics.
talk: I will sing you a story of two princes, Ragnar and Rutger, and a dead king.

name: tracker
description: You see an experienced ranger looking at some tracks on the ground.
talk: If you'll excuse me, I am looking for someone.

name: traveler
description: You see a traveler who is a long way from home.
talk: hey, this place is great...  I've never been here before

name: barmaid
description: You see a beautiful woman taking orders and serving drinks.
talk: What'll ya have?  Special today's on dwarven ale.  Have a mug.

name: dwarven outcast
description: You see a dejected dwarf that's been ostricized by his society.
talk: Leave me alone...I'm rather upset right now.

name: dwarven miner
description: You see a short fellow with a miner's pick.
talk: There's gold in the hills to the west!

name: red knight
description: You see an elite elven knight of the Order of the Rose.
talk: four buttons must be used seven times in combination to lower the drawbridge

name: grey knight
description: You see a supurb knight of the Order of the Sword.
talk: Read the papyras scroll in the library for information on elven runes.

name: white knight
description: You see a powerful knight from the Order of the Crown
talk: The drawbridge opens only with the proper combination of buttons pressed.

name: archer
description: You see a skilled elven archer with his trusty bow.
talk: What do you want?

name: marksman archer
description: You see an expert archer practicing her accuracy.
talk: Please be quiet when I'm practicing.

name: sharpshooter archer
description: You see an elven archer that's so good, she seldom misses.
talk: Give me a good bow and arrow and I'll clip a fly off your nose from 10 meters.

name: alligator
description: You see a long, green lizard slithering towards you in the water.

name: mechanical rabbit

name: maiden

description: You see a tri-horned dinosaur with a large bone shield protecting its head.

name: copper dragon
description: The saddle on the beast is made of black leather trimmed with silver.
talk: let's be back by dinner time, ok?

name: mountain troll
description: The troll is wild-eyed and slathering at the mouth.
talk: gotta remember - it's rape, pillage, THEN burn, in that order.

name: the Witch of Kayleigh
description: She may be the ugliest woman you have ever seen.
talk: your liver will go nicely in the soup

name: Silventh the Warlock
description: He looks to be about 20 years old, with a powerful muscular body.
talk: you like my new body?  An adventurer like yourself brought it to me

name: black cat
description: The cat has a murderous snarl and extended claws.

name: ghostly armormaster
description: The shade of a large and burly armormaster swirls throughout the armory.
talk: Silventh himself was responsible for my death.  Kill him, that I may rest

name: the sludge monster
description: the geletanous monster quivers and extends an eyestalk to look at you.
talk: I alone guard the key to Kayleigh.

name: gray cat
description: The gray cat has large, intelligent eyes, and looks imploring at you.
talk: meoow

name: Brownhaven guard
description: He is burly and dumb, but he takes his job very seriously.
talk: do you have your papers in order?

name: the Hydrapede
description: She is a thick-skinned water monster, with twelve arms.

name: aboleth
description: You see a amphibious creature with flailing, venomous tentacles.

name: large aboleth
description: You see a huge, amphibious creature with flailing, venomous tentacles.

name: baby aboleth
description: You see a smaller, amphibious creature which seems less developed.
talk: I'm the baby!  Gotta love me!

name: the Power Ranger
description: You see a asexual human dressed in a tight Spandex (tm) outfit.
talk: Touch my monkey!...err...if you can find it...

name: angry aboleth
description: You see angry, amphibious creature swinging it's tentacles towards you.
talk: die, ugly frogs!

name: Destroyer
description: He's a burly dwarf with a big hammer.
talk: To succeed you must work hard.

name: transparent image of Elise
description: The fading image looks like it is trying to tell you something.
talk: be sure you trade me the crystal.  Do not give it to me.  And I thank thee.

name: caretaker trainer
description: He looks like he might be helpful, if asked the correct questions.
talk: Talk to me about INTRO and HELP to get your lesson started.

name: castle guard
description: He wears the uniform of the castle, and carries a heavy trunchion.
talk: Are you a supporter of the Prince?

name: lieutenant of the guard
description: He has medals all the way across his chest.
talk: You have business here in the castle?

name: barracks guard
description: he is bored with this job of standing in a damp corridor.
talk: citizens are not allowed in the barracks

name: weaponsmith
description: He is a burly dwarf, and a member of the armormaster's corp.
talk: Only Prince Ragnar is entitled to the throne at Lyanden.

name: knight of the chrysanthemum
description: he is a holy knight who believes in Ragnar's cause.
talk: my prince, Ragnar the brave, will win with God's help.

name: weapons wizard
description: He is a tiny elf, barely half a meter in height.
talk: mutter

name: Trokkawilff
description: Trokkawilff's shade smiles evilly as he stands between you and the door.
talk: ah, you can see me!  Good.  That means you can feel me also

name: Trokkawilff's animated flaming dagger
description: The flaming dagger hovers in mid-air, aimed at a spot between your legs.
talk: I remember the good old days....

name: octowolf
description: You see an eight legged and eight eyed wolf-like monster.
talk: gggrrrr

name: green slime
description: The slime is disgusting, but very tenacious.

name: Vertinio
description: An ancient mage, long past the age of retirement.  He knows earth realm magic.
talk: Although my speciality is earth realm, I have mastered the others as well.

name: the Abbot
description: Short, and rather rotund, he wears a hair shirt and woolen gray robe.
talk: All good fighters for Ragnar may receive my blessings.  Kneel, mighty warrior.

name: the bellringer
description: Huge and dull-eyed, he stares at you suspicously.
talk: the brothers have taught me that I must kill evil.  Are you evil?

name: knight
description: he has a white rose emblazened on his armor.
talk: you must be pure of heart to attain the highest ranks.

name: knight
description: He bears a standard with a picture of an eye looking from a peach tree.
talk: the fruit of your victory is sweeter when it comes through rightfulness.

name: knight
description: he has a crimson sash tied to his helmet.
talk: only those with white souls and red blood may join us.  You are not ready

name: acolyte
description: He looks a little tipsy, and offers you a drink of wine from a silve chalice.
talk: shhh...  not so loud.  The brothers will hear us

name: cowled clerk
description: You cannot see his face, but he stretches a bony hand toward you.
talk: there are certain formalitys we must go through for you to rescind your pledge

name: Prince Ragnar
description: He is resplendent in a black velvet suit piped in silver.
talk: Speak with me a little before you take your oath.

name: healing mage
description: She is a cleric-mage in a snow-white robe.  She carries a healing wand.
talk: I know several healing spells and wish you well.  What do you desire?

name: the shade of Lady Vickers
description: You see a dark shadow wearing a white gown.  She is playing a violin.
talk: If I stop playing, the forces of darkness will come back.

name: banshee
description: The banshee is simply a presense which you cannot see, but you certainly hear!
talk: EEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!!!!!!!!

name: ghostly butler
description: You can see right through him!  He is studying a note on the table.
talk: I can't read this without my glasses.

name: Travis
description: He is a human dignatary to Kista, come to help solve some problems.
talk: I would rather be exploring the mountains north of here.

name: blue-coated guard
description: You see one of the tower guards form the Blue Regiment.
talk: Visitors are very restricted as to where they may go.

name: Evan
description: Evan is a gnarled little gnome with a misshapened, pointed head.
talk: What are you looking at?  Are you going to buy a potion or not?

name: dirty begger
description: He hasn't bathed in weeks, and stares at you with his one good eye.
talk: do ye have some gold for an old adventurer?  I was once as you are now.

name: scholar
description: You see an odd looking human, wearing a billowing black gown and a mortor.
talk: do you know where I might find a text on necrophilia?

name: book clerk
description: The clerk is busy restacking the shelves with books.
talk: can't you see I'm busy?  Besides. I only work here, I don't answer questions.

name: the Curator
description: The Curator is a grey-haired little elf with a book under his arm.
talk: are you looking for knowledge or wealth?

name: black-robed monk
description: You see a monk wielding a mace.
talk: begone!  You people take up too much of the oracle's time with foolishness.

name: guardian monk
description: You see a well muscled young monk wielding a cleric's mace.
talk: join our order if you wish to speak to the oracle!  Else leave us alone.

name: Veratus the Oracle
description: Veratus has the naked body of a young woman, and the face and head of an owl.
talk: Elise in the Towers will send you on a quest.  Return there for your reward.

name: small Gray Owl
description: Veratus appears to you as a small owl, almost transparent in appearance.
talk: if I like the subject of your question, I will answer it.

name: Snow-White Owl
description: Veratus has taken the form of a large, snow-white owl.
talk: please, ask me another question.  If I like it...

name: Great-Horned Owl
description: The Great-Horned Owl is Veratus, in one of her many forms.
talk: I am interested in your quest, if you ask the right question.

name: Kuroth the Demon
description: He is hideous, with dripping fangs and red-rimmed eyes.  He looms over you.
talk: so.  You have come as a champion for Elise?  She has sent many to die here.

name: image of Elise
description: The fading image looks like it is trying to tell you something.
talk: be sure you trade me the crystal.  Do not give it to me.  And I thank thee.

name: Lieutenant of the Guards
description: he's burly, mean and drunk, and he has a sword in each hand.
talk: if you aren't the pizza guy, you're gonna be the topping for it.  hic.

name: drunken guard
description: He's so drunk he can hardly see you, but he has a razor sharp halbard.
talk: where's the pizza?  go back and get it!  goddamn, can't do anything right.

name: barbarian guard
description: He stifles a yawn as he looks at you.
talk: personally, I don't think you can do it.

name: barbarian guard
description: He watches you carefully, ready to throw you back out the door.
talk: don't waste my time.  You're never going to get through me.

name: barbarian guard
description: He's rough, tough and eats live rattlesnakes.  He glares at you.
talk: Get the hell outtta here before I lose my appetite.  *spit*

name: barbarian warrior
description: he is a huge speciman of a man, with bulging muscles and a suspicous look.
talk: trust only what you can see, and never put your faith in magic.

name: flower nymph
description: You see a tiny gossamer-like creature with pale yellow wings.
talk: the jacintha seeds are very good for your health, but beware the side effects.

name: hobbit adventurer
description: You see a hobbit with hairy feet wearing good leather armor.
talk: my comrades and I have seen some exciting things to the north.

name: kitchen helper
description: You see a smaller than normal dwarf rushing about the kitchen.
talk: customers aren't allowed here in the kitchen, so get out.

name: Mother Granovetter
description: She must be the oldest and fattest and uglist dwarf you have ever seen!
talk: we make many healing potions from our vegetable garden.

name: Heber Granovetter
description: Heber, blind and crazy, drools as he reaches for the sound you make...
talk: hehe, so they dropped another goodie down here for ol' Heber.

name: rum salesman
description: You see a stout little dwarf who works for the Uland Rum Company.
talk: Now, I can give you a discount for cash, if you don't want a receipt.

name: shit-eating worm
description: The worm is pretty big, about two meters long, and looks at you hungrily.

name: Blue Warrior
description: You see a very large humanoid who has painted his face and body bright blue.
talk: welcome.  If you are worthy of advancement, you will defeat me.

name: Green Warrior
description: This mighty warrior is dressed in green silk from head to toe.
talk: I welcome you to the next level, but you must defeat me first.

name: Red Warrior
description: He is swathed in blood-red chain mail, and his face is hidden from you.
talk: I do not believe you can defeat me, but I wish you well.  You may begin...

name: the Jinsuti Master
description: He is a muscular man of unknown age.  He wears silk and a fighter's harness.
talk: I must ask you to bring me certain things to complete your training.

name: blue hydrabeast
description: You see a scaly, grotesque female water beast, and she looks hungry!

name: green hydrabeast
description: You see an ugly, scaly male water beast, waiting for its dinner.

name: hextril
description: The hextril has six acid spewing tentacles, and weighs about ten pounds.

name: large hextril
description: A mother hextril!  Six acid-spewing tentacles and a hungry mouth.

name: drunken nightwatchman
description: He has a bottle of rum in one hand and a short sword in the other.
talk: where did you come from?  HELP!   HELP!   Invaders are amongst us!

name: yeoman
description: You see a dumb oaf wearing a hodge-podge of armor and weapons.
talk: I ain't scared o' nuthin.  I already killed a man, so there.

name: Commander Franchot
description: You see a tall paladin in gleaming black and silver armor.
talk: I'm sorry, but I only accept the very best as volunteers for the Black Guard.

name: brown-robed monk
description: The monk wears a long, brown robe, sandals and a single glove.
talk: have you dedicated your life to a purpose, child?

name: catapult officer
description: The officer is concerned with his heavy equipment.
talk: the accuracy of our catapults needs improvement.  Ya got any ideas?

name: Apstone
description: He is an ancient old grey beard, bent with age and almost blind.
talk: do not stay in this room very long, my young friend, else you will look as me.

name: janitor
description: Just an old guy with a bucket and mop.  What did you expect?
talk: mutter.  Someday I'm gonna kill one of 'em for steppin' on my clean floor.

name: bombardier
description: bombardiers wear a distinctive leather harness, with many buckles on it.
talk: with a good catapult, I can knock the eyes out of a newt at 100 meters.

name: masked cleric
description: You see a hooded and masked cleric wearing a dull black robe.
talk: repeat these words if you desire to leave this kingdom:  rescind to rutger.

name: Prince Rutger
description: The Prince is resplendent in a blue uniform with gold piping.
talk: speak to me before I accept your oath.  Let us talk awhile.  Please sit.

name: Rutger
description: Prince Rutger scowls and awaits your decision.
talk: bah.  Do not speak to me.  Ask the cleric what you must do to leave.

name: Ragnar
description: Prince Ragnar's face betrays his disgust for you.
talk: Never speak to me again.  Talk to the clerk, so that he may remove your name.

name: Tragirsha
description: Tragirsha is a huge, toadlike creature with the face of a fat, ugly woman.
talk: I can tell you many things of this land we call Mordor.

name: Gorgon the Demon
description: Gorgon, the blinded demon, listens quietly for your footsteps.
talk: step closer and take my hand that I might know you.  Are you also blind?

name: acid imp
description: The acid imp is a tiny, red demon which spits acid at you from ballon cheeks!

name: Glabor, King of the Trolls
description: You see the biggest troll you have ever seen in your life.  He glares at you.
talk: I need new bones to increase the size of my throne room.  Are you a volunteer?

name: bartender
description: The bartender is an ugly troll mixing drinks and leering at the females.
talk: buy something or get out.  I can't waste my time with sissies.

name: troll priestess
description: She has pointed teeth and large, red eyes.  She also has bad breath.
talk: wrakk tchk's ssst?  Dree ki tchk amser klatc?  WAGG?

name: musician
description: This musician is a small troll carrying an odd looking musical instrument.
talk: you people have no appreciation for the six tone musical scale.  bah.

name: gnome
description: You see a short and red-faced person with large hands and a great belly.
talk: what are you looking at?  Got nothing better to do than stare?
